Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.04,0:00:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍新来的Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.44,0:00:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代号名是刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他作为GN-001的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的驾驶员特性到达了基准值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是维塔选中了他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好的么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都做好了相当的觉悟而加入组织 成为了Gundam机师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与年龄大小无关
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代号名 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能狙击到平流层那一面的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.67,0:00:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想用Gundam来改变世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:01:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 从托勒密传来了特别暗号通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同国联军拟造GN驱动器搭载MS开始交战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上内容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界会眷顾哪一边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是国联 还是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你降到地上 导致战斗分散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 为什么他非死不可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 他会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.26,0:03:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人还在 有闲情哭诉的话 还不如帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 对不起 菲露特 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是哈罗的错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出击的27架机体中 只有11架归舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕获的机体也失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 Gundam的新能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛奈金大佐 我建议从现宙域撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去只会一味的折损兵力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞同 但国联的司令部已来指示 将向我们派遣增援
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援? 难道还有GN驱动器搭载MS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令指示 增援一到就展开第二波攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到接近本舰的GN-X
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有生存者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始机体核对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员是AEU所属 帕特利库·克拉萨瓦少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 大佐 被摆了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人担心 蠢家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带翅膀的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有受到我的脑量子波影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实施了遮断处理吗 还是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 在下一次战斗中做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是完全体的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能输给残缺的实验体E-57
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照指示 发出了散播GN粒子的卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这样能骗到敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暂时放心 小行星周围正在被监视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样也得尽力而为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 Gundam的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios如果把飞行部件卸除的话还可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue需要卸下外装甲 以Nadleeh形态出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专用的武器已经准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要多久才能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最少也得8小时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在6小时内完成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现战力 能够期待的只有强袭用荚舱和Exia 还有GN兵装
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为救命草的TRANS-AM也有使用时间限制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·诺莉艾卡 请提交下一次的作战计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 你想战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要歼灭敌人的拟造GN驱动器搭载MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能向世界夸示我们的力量 计划就能继续进行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风险太大了 敌人派遣增援的可能性也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这不仅仅是我自己的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机师们的全体意见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷鲁亚和刹那也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下去 的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人把洛克昂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的双亲和妹妹都卷入了KPSA的自爆恐怖事件死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我干掉家族的仇人 解除心中的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出性命 向敌人开火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你怕死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是对神的亵渎行为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在死的尽头 没有神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了现在 我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们天行者的存在本身 不就有了意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在本身 那就是活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩负着死去同胞的心愿 面对世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是靠什么神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要凭我自己的意志…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从第34观测舰发来通信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现4支不断远离小行星的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令小行星周围哨戒的部队予以确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是佯动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方有机影靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这个机体是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是窃取天行者的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样么 刹那他们选择了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟噢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也只能这么干了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢 菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 写给天国的爸爸和妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特的双亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兆头不好啊 写什么遗书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我会活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说暂时不会再见面了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要这个气势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和洛克昂做了约定的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要守护好那个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也写个信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在殖民地的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说只是养母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美好的回忆 什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像逃一样离家出走 被维达选中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实确实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里希特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲过去是轨道升降机的技术人员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小时候的太阳能发电的纷争中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个个死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家各有各的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为经历了这些 大家才加入天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 像这样相互说自己的事情是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为有守密义务 但是事到如今嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.14,0:10:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh的整备怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是对于又没有TRANS-AM系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子贮藏量也少的Nadleeh
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算那样也要上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂的仇 我不报不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑还是不要太发热
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.58,0:10:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不那样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特·库蕾伊丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.87,0:10:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给洛克昂的信写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.54,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂收
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.50,0:10:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 你有要写信的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:11:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.48,0:11:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以哈罗 你要陪在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·斯特拉特斯的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪陪他 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.33,0:11:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E传感器有反应 捕捉到敌人部队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.76,0:11:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对速度0235
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离战斗可能宙域…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人部队总数是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是其中有一架非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常大?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示在显示屏上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是战斗舰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载了拟造太阳炉的MA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子束来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然从这么远的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一粒子输出部被击中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.78,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子供给全部切换到第二输出部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二波攻击来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭荚舱出击 目标为敌MA
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强袭荚舱 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特 让托勒密躲入附近卫星的阴影中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios和Nadleeh直接从荚舱出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责保卫托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按作战计划 同时从两个方向对敌太空船发起攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机以卫星为掩护接近敌舰 实施打击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.86,0:13:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的战功由我拿下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.05,0:13:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方有急速接近的机影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.37,0:13:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给MA就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要做一个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人MS部队从左右两侧袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会让你们再前进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你那半裸的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用TRANS-AM还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这台机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 阿雷鲁亚 我现在还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验体E-57!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入射程了 开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field? 那样的出力是怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这一击又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 是谁干的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三第四荚舱遭到重创
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右侧受损极其严重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭E-20到E-68号闸门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐 医疗室被击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样就走了 这个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系统发生故障
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field无法展开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转移到强袭用荚舱去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不迎击的话就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络伊昂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh 攻击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙真幸运啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有到死的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了计划 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你们干的好事 这些混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还活着么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 命中吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames的太阳炉有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像连接状况出了点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那种数据没…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜到了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一架敌机正朝这里迫近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不想再惹菲露特生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.75,0:17:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想绕到死角去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荚舱从托勒密号脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,状况怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克丽丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克丽丝!里希特!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克丽丝!里希特!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克丽丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时和父母一起被卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半的身体就成了这副样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会活下去么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会死呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨蛋啊 我这人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么好的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没眼光呢 我真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特…回答我…克丽丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克丽丝 平安无事吧 里希特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特在么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再对装扮细心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着洛克昂的份一起 活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让世界…改变吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克丽丝!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里希特!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克丽丝蒂娜·雪拉!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击无效
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.66,0:21:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就迎头冲上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接攻击了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.20,0:21:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨的伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的亡灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我亚里桑德罗·科纳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来把你们超度到新世界去吧!
